Can you help me find some car rental companies in LA that have SUVs available? Also, could you recommend me the one with the highest rating? Just let me know the company name and its rating. Thanks a bunch!

This will be followed by checking the types of cars available at each company to find the available SUVs. Finally, I will retrieve the ratings and reviews for each company to determine which has the highest rating.
</function_thought>

<function_call>[get_all_car_rental_companies_in_city(city="Los Angeles")]</function_call>
